  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n陸相、南方軍総司令官、元帥陸軍大将、<a href=\"../p/tmasatak.html\">寺内正毅</a>の長男 "
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"04t.html\">一覧　（タ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　山口県出身。首相・伯爵・元帥陸軍大将、<a href=\"../p/tmasatak.html\">寺内正毅</a>の長男。陸士卒、陸大卒。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　台湾軍司令官など歴任後、<a href=\"../1936/02226ji.html\">二・二六事件</a>直後、陸相候補となり、組閣に大干渉。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　陸相時、<a href=\"../1936/05bukan.html\">軍部大臣現役武官制の復活</a>など、軍部の発言権を飛躍的に拡大させる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　陸軍を批判する<a href=\"../p/hkunimat.html\">浜田国松議員</a>と<a href=\"../1937/01kappu.html\">「割腹問答」</a>を展開。内閣に懲罰解散を要求し辞任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　大戦中は、南方軍総司令官として南方作戦を指揮、<a href=\"../1945/08gyoku.html\">敗戦</a>後サイゴンで死亡。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
